   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">You can exclude products or categories from the qualification rows. The <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Exclude</b> button is enabled after the products or categories are added.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">To exclude a product and category:</p>
      <ol class="- topic/ol ">
         <li class="- topic/li ">Click <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Exclude.</b>The Exclude Products page pop-up appears as follows and it is not editable.<fig class="- topic/fig ">
               <image height="250"
                      placement="break"
                      href="../attachments/108500817/108500810.png"
                      class="- topic/image "/>
            </fig>
         </li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">Select the categories in the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Included Products</b> tab.</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">Click <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Exclude</b> and <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Save</b>.<p class="- topic/p ">You cannot view the excluded categories or products in the Category/Products tab but you can view the excluded categories in the Excluded Products tab.</p>
         </li>
      </ol>
